---

<section id="contact" class="section contact-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Contáctame</h2>

    <div class="contact-wrapper">
      <div
        class="contact-info animate-fade-in"
        style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;"
      >
        <h3 class="contact-subtitle">
          Hablemos sobre tu próximo proyecto
        </h3>
        <p class="contact-description">
          Si estás buscando un desarrollador FullStack enfocado en soluciones de
          impacto o te interesa integrar inteligencia artificial a tus procesos,
          ¡no dudes en escribirme!
        </p>

        <div
          class="contact-methods"
          style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 1.5rem;"
        >
          <a
            href="mailto:franklyndev20@gmail.com"
            class="method-item glass-panel"
          >
            <i class="bx bx-envelope"></i>
            <div style="text-align: left;">
              <h4>Email</h4>
              <span>franklyndev20@gmail.com</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/franklyn-ramirez-tinedo-88489b350/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="method-item glass-panel"
          >
            <i class="bx bxl-linkedin"></i>
            <div style="text-align: left;">
              <h4>LinkedIn</h4>
              <span>Franklyn Ramirez</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <div class="method-item glass-panel">
            <i class="bx bx-map"></i>
            <div style="text-align: left;">
              <h4>Ubicación</h4>
              <span>Perú</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-section {
    background: linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      var(--color-bg) 0%,
      var(--color-bg-secondary) 100%
    );
  }

  .contact-wrapper {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .contact-subtitle {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .contact-description {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
    .contact-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .contact-wrapper .contact-methods {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .method-item {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
    }
  }
</style>
